{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264240/extras/StoreGIF_6.gif?t=1728090893\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DESCEND INTO DARKNESS - DEMO</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take your first steps into the terrifying world of Dr. Gloom\u2019s Lab\u2122. In this demo, you\u2019ll get a taste of the full experience\u2014exploring the eerie beginning of Jaxon Blair's journey. Venture into the depths, face off against gruesome mutants, and get hands-on with the crafting system that could be the key to your survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SURVIVAL BEGINS NOW</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover a glimpse of the dangers ahead as you explore the first segments of the lab, craft traps, and battle against horrifying mutants. Tension builds as you begin to feel the presence of something much worse. As the footsteps grow louder and a deep, bone-chilling growl closes in... the demo ends, leaving you wanting more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">EXPERIENCE THE TERROR</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this first look, you\u2019ll witness the atmospheric tension, beautiful but disturbing environments, and fast-paced first-person combat. Powered by Unreal Engine 5, the demo delivers a taste of the suspense, the challenges, and the dark narrative that awaits in the full release.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264240/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728090893","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264240/page.bg.jpg?t=1728090893","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264240/90b05e20f0ed074a327bcd71745de48d79a32506/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728090893","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264240/90b05e20f0ed074a327bcd71745de48d79a32506/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1728090893","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"Prepare to encounter blood, bones, and body bags in the depths of Dr. Gloom's laboratory. Your journey will be fraught with the remnants of failed experiments and the twisted forms of mutated creatures. Enter with caution, for every corner may hold a new horror to face."},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264240/extras/StoreGIF_6.gif?t=1728090893\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">DESCEND INTO DARKNESS - DEMO</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take your first steps into the terrifying world of Dr. Gloom\u2019s Lab\u2122. In this demo, you\u2019ll get a taste of the full experience\u2014exploring the eerie beginning of Jaxon Blair's journey. Venture into the depths, face off against gruesome mutants, and get hands-on with the crafting system that could be the key to your survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SURVIVAL BEGINS NOW</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover a glimpse of the dangers ahead as you explore the first segments of the lab, craft traps, and battle against horrifying mutants. Tension builds as you begin to feel the presence of something much worse. As the footsteps grow louder and a deep, bone-chilling growl closes in... the demo ends, leaving you wanting more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">EXPERIENCE THE TERROR</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this first look, you\u2019ll witness the atmospheric tension, beautiful but disturbing environments, and fast-paced first-person combat. Powered by Unreal Engine 5, the demo delivers a taste of the suspense, the challenges, and the dark narrative that awaits in the full release.</p>","developers":["Dogan Development"],"fullgame":{"appid":"2975470","name":"Dr. Gloom\u2019s Lab\u2122"},"genres":[{"description":"